text: Novobakayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Krasnovoskhodsky Selsoviet, Iglinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 38 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 88 km from Iglino, 3 km from Krasny Voskhod. == References == Category:Rural localities in Iglinsky District
title: Novobakayevo
